    "course_title": "THE RUSSIAN WAR ON UKRAINE: CAUSES AND CONSEQUENCES",
    "description": "Examines causes and consequences of the Russian invasion and war on Ukraine. Analyzes the war using concepts in comparative politics (e.g., regime type, national identity, and domestic politics in Ukraine and Russia) and international relations (e.g., international security, institutions and norms, sanctions and trade, migration and human rights).",
